==When not to use this template==
Remember to "avoid using smaller font sizes in elements that already use a smaller font size, such as infoboxes, navboxes and reference sections", per [[Wikipedia:格式手冊/親和力|MOS:ACCESS#Font size]] and [[Wikipedia:格式手冊/文字格式|MOS:SMALLFONT]]. Using this template within an infobox or a navbox reduces the text size to about 75%, which is smaller than the 85% limit prescribed by the MOS guideline.

